63, \"to\": 1787}, {\"ngram\": \"their own purposes\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, that explains the significant difference between the Olympic symbol and the Paralympic one.\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 1908, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the significant difference\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1857}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic symbol\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1884}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:When do the Tokyo 2020 Paralympics start?\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1961, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1932, \"end\": 1954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Paralympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tokyo 2020 Paralympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Paralympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Paralympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1932, \"end\": 1937, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999932720637706, \"rank\": 6.727232493485292e-06, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Team GB Paralympics legend David Weir: 'I feel a lot calmer and less angry at 42' ArrowMORE:Athlete 'not disabled enough' for Paralympics is considering amputating a leg Follow Metro across our social channels, onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram Share your views in the comments below Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 2368, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1973, \"end\": 1980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999427926870718, \"rank\": 5.66088291569414e-05, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"htt